[[File:Halasana.jpg|thumb|upright=1.4|Halasana]] {{Contains Indic text}} '''Halasana''' ({{IPAc-en|h|ʌ|ˈ|l|æ|s|ʌ|n|ə}};<ref>{{cite book |last1=Budilovsky |first1=Joan |last2=Adamson |first2=Eve |title=The complete idiot's guide to yoga |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=b5pE8-Oyly0C |accessdate=11 April 2011 |edition=2 |year=2000 |publisher=Penguin |isbn=978-0-02-863970-3 |page=175}}</ref> {{lang-sa|हलासन}}; [[IAST]]: ''Halāsana'') or '''Plough Pose'''<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.yogajournal.com/poses/479 | title = Yoga Journal - Plow Pose | accessdate = 2011-04-09}}</ref> is an [[asana]].
==Etymology== The name comes from the Sanskrit words '<nowiki/>''hala'<nowiki/>'' (हला) meaning "plow" and '<nowiki/>''asana''' (आसन) meaning "posture" or "seat".<ref name="(Swami.)1985">{{cite book |author=Sivananda (Swami.) |title=Health and hatha yoga |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Rf7aAAAAMAAJ |accessdate=9 April 2011 |date=June 1985 |publisher=Divine Life Society |isbn=978-0-949027-03-0 |page=128}}</ref>
==Cautions== This asana can put significant strain on the [[cervical spine]], which does not normally undergo this type of [[stress (mechanics)|stress]], and can cause injury if not performed properly.<ref name="Inc.1983">{{cite book |author=Active Interest Media, Inc. |title=Yoga Journal |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8usDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA7 |accessdate=9 April 2011 |date=February 1983 |publisher=Active Interest Media, Inc. |page=7 |issn=0191-0965}}</ref><ref name="Robin2002">{{cite book |last=Robin |first=Mel |title=A Physiological Handbook for Teachers of Yogasana |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xyJEDt9LrGsC&pg=PA516 |accessdate=9 April 2011 |date=May 2002 |publisher=Wheatmark, Inc. |isbn=978-1-58736-033-6 |page=516}}</ref><ref name="Robin2009">{{cite book |last=Robin |first=Mel |title=A Handbook for Yogasana Teachers: The Incorporation of Neuroscience, Physiology, and Anatomy Into the Practice |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=L3qJshT_K8UC&pg=PA835 |accessdate=9 April 2011 |year=2009 |publisher=Wheatmark, Inc. |isbn=978-1-58736-708-3 |page=835}}</ref>
